high_descs: Go forward and hang a right, go to the counter, hang a right, go the the dining table on the right.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the table in front of the coffee cup.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the counter where the toaster is.
Cut the potato into slices that is on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the microwave on the other side of the room.
Open the microwave, put the knife inside, close the microwave.
Turn around, go forward to the counter with the toaster on it that is just past the stove on the right.
Pick up a slice of the potato that is on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the microwave at the other end of the room.
Put the potato in the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the potato when it is done cooking.
Turn around, go to the dining table and hang a right, go to the fridge, turn right and face the counter with the toaster on it.
Put the potato on the counter next to the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked potato on a counter.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the end of the table, then make another right and walk to the middle of the table, and turn and face the table to your right.
Pick up the butter knife that is in front of the white, coffee mug.
Turn to your right and walk to the small kitchen counter, between the refrigerator and the stove.
Cut the potato on the counter, in front of the toaster, into slices.
Turn to your right and walk across the room to the microwave, on the kitchen counter.
Place the knife inside the microwave, towards the front.
Turn around and walk across the room, towards the table, and turn to your right at the toaster.
Pick up a piece of the potato previously sliced.
Turn to your right and walk back to the microwave, across the room.
Place the potato slice into the microwave, heat it, then remove it from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room to the refrigerator, then turn around so that you are facing the side of the toaster, next to the refrigerator.
Place a heated potato slice on the counter, in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm potato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, go straight to the start of the counter, turn right, go forward, turn right to face the round black table.
Take the knife from the left of the black table.
Turn around, go straight and turn left at the counter to the left of the oven. Go straight to the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn right, go forward to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the counter to the left of the oven, where the potato is. Go to the counter.
Take a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn right, go forward to the microwave.
Cook the potato in the microwave, take the potato from the microwave.
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the fridge, go to the fridge, turn right to face the counter.
Put the slice of potato on the counter near the corner of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right then right around the table and face the round table to your right.
Pick up the silver knife from the table.
Turn around and head towards the counter with the potato to your left.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Turn right and head towards the microwave on the counter in front of you.
Put the knife in the microwave and close it.
Turn around and face the counter with the potato to your right.
Take a potato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn right and head towards the microwave on the counter in front of you.
Heat up the potato in the microwave, take it out and close the microwave.
Turn around and then right to be by the counter with the toaster.
Put the potato slice on the counter by the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm potato on the counter by the toaster.

high_descs: Turn right towards the counter and then turn right towards the circle table to your right.
Pick up the knife in front of the white cup on the table.
Turn around, take a step forward, and then turn left towards the toaster on the counter.
Slice the potato in front of the toaster into several pieces.
Turn right and head towards the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and head towards the toaster on your right.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn right and head towards the microwave.
Heat up the potato and take it back out  of the microwave.
Turn around and head towards the toaster on your right.
Place the potato slice in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm potato slice in front of the toaster.
